oai_dc:dc.dc:title: NCAA Champions
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Athletes; Soccer; Women
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Coached by Gareth O'Sullivan, Christian Brothers' Lady Bucs won the NCAA Division II Women's Soccer Championship by beating Nebraska-Omaha 2-1 at the Virginia Beach Sportsplex.
